data.description: Set amidst a gorgeous tree canopy in the sought-after Lanceford Creek Plantation community within Oyster Bay, this handsome lakefront POOL home is located on over a 1/2-acre. Features include whole-house generator, gas appliances, upgraded kitchen with gas cooktop and custom cabinetry, crown molding, wood floors, summer kitchen, and a fenced in backyard. Master-suite and primary guest bedroom are located on the first floor. The second floor features an open balcony, 3 additional bedrooms, and a media room with a kitchenette. Lanceford Creek Plantation is known for its true estate size lots, amazing sunsets over Lanceford Creek, & well-kept lawns & landscaping among homeowners. Oyster Bay Yacht club social membership available with access to a community dock, boat slips, restaurant, bar, gym, & pool.
